Dark Scream




A stasis pod headed straight to earth. His name was Dark Scream. A 
group of Decepticons and predcons tried to make a a transform that 
was both Star scream and Megatron. After something went wrong they 
had to get rid of him. They did not know his spark survived in his 
body. after crashing the stasis pod in Cuba the pod started emitting 
a Decepticon signal.
